flowchart LR
  User((End User))
  Admin((Admin))

  P1[1.0 Auth Service]
  P2[2.0 Document Processing]
  P3[3.0 Chat Query Engine]
  P4[4.0 Analytics & Admin]

  D1[(D1 User Store)]
  D2[(D2 Document Metadata)]
  D3[(D3 Vector Store)]
  D4[(D4 Chat History)]

  User -->|credentials| P1
  P1 -->|profile + token| User
  P1 <--> D1

  User -->|documents| P2
  P2 -->|status| User
  P2 <--> D2
  P2 <--> D3

  User -->|question| P3
  P3 -->|answer + citations| User
  P3 <--> D3
  P3 <--> D4

  Admin -->|dashboard request| P4
  P4 -->|reports + user insights| Admin
  P4 <--> D1
  P4 <--> D2
  P4 <--> D4
